we were checking in advance for null pointers, etc -- we were.  The place
where it hangs is when printw() is first called.  ckuusx.c, 26 Oct 96.

Fixed a bad bug in \freplace() that had been there forever; namely, when the
match string and the replacement strings were different lengths, the result
